data.description: Wonderful home in the quiet neighborhood of Huntington. 4 bedroom, 2 full bath split-Level home  offers ample living as well as storage space. The main floor features LR, DR, & kitchen. Living room & dining room feature newly refinished hardwood floors with a slider that opens onto a nice deck and fenced in backyard, while the kitchen boasts new appliances. The upstairs offers 3 BR's and 1 full bath, lower level has wonderful family room with wood burning fireplace, full bathroom & 4th BR that would make an excellent office. New roof installed in 2017. Home has been given a fresh coat of paint through out, just waiting for you to put on the finishing touches. Home is convenient to I-95, Christiana Mall, Christiana Hospital & other main stays.
